  <brief_title>ETREAT Study on Effectiveness of Botulinum Toxin Type A Injections to Treat Post-stroke Upper and/or Lower Limb Spasticity</brief_title>
  <acronym>ETREAT</acronym>
  <official_title>ETREAT Study: A Prospective Observational Study to Evaluate the Effectiveness of Botulinum Toxin Type A (BoNT-A) Injections in Patients With Post-stroke Upper and/or Lower Limb Spasticity in the Early Stage of Spasticity Development.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
